high_descs: Turn left and face the cabinets above the coffee maker.
Open the cabinet and take the plate from the cabinet.
Put the plate in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick up the plate.
Go left and face the microwave above the stove.
Put the plate in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn and go to the cupboard above the coffee maker.
Take a plate out of the cupboard.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the plate in the sink.
Pick up the plate in the sink and go to the microwave.
Put the plate in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed plate in the microwave.

high_descs: turn left towards the coffee maker
take out the plate in the cupboard above the coffee maker
rinse the plate in the sink
drop the plate inside the microwave
anns.task_desc: drop a clean plate inside the microwave
